sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant App as Streamlit or API
    participant G as LangGraph
    participant TP as Travelpayouts
    participant L as LLM

    U->>App: Текст запроса
    App->>G: run_travel_planning_graph / invoke
    G->>L: extract_trip_query
    G->>TP: search_routes / hotels (если scope)
    G->>L: suggest_city_attractions
    G->>L: generate_travel_itinerary
    G-->>App: final_markdown
    App-->>U: План поездки
